// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Account-deletion rules fragment (App Store Guideline 5.1.1(v))
// MERGE the clauses below into your live `firestore.rules` in Firebase Console.
//
// Without these clauses the in-app delete flow (`profile/delete-account.tsx` →
// `lib/firestore/accountDeletion.ts`) will hit `permission-denied` and fail
// halfway through, leaving orphan data behind. That breaks Apple compliance.
//
// The `isCoupleMember(coupleId)` helper assumes the existing rules already use
// the same name. If yours is named differently, swap accordingly.
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

